{color:#ff0000}*current situation:*{color}

when a user creates a statement (no matter if the itinerary is created manually or from a Cytric travel source) there is
 * breakfast deduction on the first travel day 
 * no breakfast deduction on the last travel day

 

!image-2022-12-27-12-37-11-674.png!

 

{color:#ff0000}*Situation as it should be in the future:*{color}

 
 * {color:#ff0000}statutory values{color}
 * {color:#ff0000}no breakfast deduction on the first day of the trip{color}
 * {color:#ff0000}breakfast deduction from the second day until the last day of the trip{color} 
 ** {color:#172b4d}*Examples:*{color}
 ** {color:#172b4d}*trip from 17. -18. August:* breakfast deduction *NOT* for 17. August *BUT* for 18. August{color} 
